-- More well-formedness lemmas

opaque

  -- A well-formedness lemma for _⊩ᵛ⟨_⟩_≡_.

  wf-⊩ᵛ≡ : Γ ⊩ᵛ⟨ l ⟩ A ≡ B → Γ ⊩ᵛ⟨ l ⟩ A × Γ ⊩ᵛ⟨ l ⟩ B
  wf-⊩ᵛ≡ A≡B =
      ⊩ᵛ⇔⊩ᵛ≡ .proj₂ (trans-⊩ᵛ≡ A≡B (sym-⊩ᵛ≡ A≡B))
