opaque

  -- A well-formedness lemma for _⊩ᵛ⟨_⟩_≡_∷_.

  wf-⊩ᵛ≡∷ : Γ ⊩ᵛ⟨ l ⟩ t ≡ u ∷ A → Γ ⊩ᵛ⟨ l ⟩ t ∷ A × Γ ⊩ᵛ⟨ l ⟩ u ∷ A
  wf-⊩ᵛ≡∷ t≡u =
      ⊩ᵛ∷⇔⊩ᵛ≡∷ .proj₂ (trans-⊩ᵛ≡∷ t≡u (sym-⊩ᵛ≡∷ t≡u))
    , ⊩ᵛ∷⇔⊩ᵛ≡∷ .proj₂ (trans-⊩ᵛ≡∷ (sym-⊩ᵛ≡∷ t≡u) t≡u)

