opaque

  -- Conversion for _⊩ᵛ⟨_⟩_∷_.

  conv-⊩ᵛ∷ :
    Γ ⊩ᵛ⟨ l ⟩ A ≡ B →
    Γ ⊩ᵛ⟨ l′ ⟩ t ∷ A →
    Γ ⊩ᵛ⟨ l ⟩ t ∷ B
  conv-⊩ᵛ∷ A≡B =
    ⊩ᵛ∷⇔⊩ᵛ≡∷ .proj₂ ∘→ conv-⊩ᵛ≡∷ A≡B ∘→ ⊩ᵛ∷⇔⊩ᵛ≡∷ .proj₁

opaque

  -- Conversion for the context for _⊩ᵛ⟨_⟩_∷_.

  conv-∙-⊩ᵛ∷ :
    Γ ⊩ᵛ⟨ l′ ⟩ A ≡ B →
    Γ ∙ A ⊩ᵛ⟨ l ⟩ t ∷ C →
    Γ ∙ B ⊩ᵛ⟨ l ⟩ t ∷ C
