opaque

  -- A lemma related to liftSubst.

  ⊩ˢ≡∷-liftSubst :
    Γ ⊩ᵛ⟨ l ⟩ A →
    Δ ⊩ˢ σ₁ ≡ σ₂ ∷ Γ →
    Δ ∙ A [ σ₁ ] ⊩ˢ liftSubst σ₁ ≡ liftSubst σ₂ ∷ Γ ∙ A
