        , neutral-⊩≡∷ (⊩ᵛ→⊩ˢ∷→⊩[] ⊩A $ wf-⊩ˢ≡∷ σ₁⇑₊≡σ₂⇑₊ .proj₁)
            (var _) (var _) ⊢0 ⊢0 (~-var ⊢0)
        )
